					<head>Majmaʻ al-baḥrayn by Muḥammad Abū Turāb</head>
					<msContents class="https://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh85129660">
						<summary>An incomplete copy of a dissertation on aspects of Sufi doctorine
							by Muḥammad Abū Turāb, who completed the work in 1215 AH (1800-1 CE). </summary>
						<msItem xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1119-item1">
							<author key="person_f8455">
								<persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Muḥammad Abū Turāb</persName>
								<persName xml:lang="fa">محمد ابو تراب</persName>
							</author>
							<title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_23356">Majmaʻ al-baḥrayn</title>
							<title xml:lang="fa">مجمع البحرین</title>
							<incipit xml:lang="fa">شرح عشق و عاشقی هم عشق گفت/ آفتاب آمد دلیل آفتاب/
								گر دلیلت باید از وی رو متاب</incipit>
							<explicit xml:lang="fa">و مرتبه ایمان به مقتضای الله ولی الذین آمنوا
								ملازم درجه ولایت است و هی کسفینة نوح من رکب...</explicit>
							<note>
								<p>The beginning starts with the 2nd part of a
										<foreign xml:lang="fa">bayt</foreign>, without any indication as to how
									many folios are missing. </p>
								<p>The date of completion is given on f. 29v as 1215 AH/1800-1 CE)
									together with the chronogram <title>Safīnah-i nijāt</title>.
								</p>
							</note>
							<textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
